{"id": 1033, "genre": 1001, "title": "为了合群，你都如何伪装过自己？", "description": "伪造出一种名为“志趣相投”的假象。（题图来自：Sam Chivers）", "record_count": 5418, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152314lLyYzIo3OhcWHQid.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-05T01:00:07Z", "options": [{"id": 85248, "content": "假装我很喜欢几个人一起吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634922}, {"id": 85760, "content": "傻傻的陪笑 找一些话题每次都会让场面冷下来 后来就再也不开口了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636622}, {"id": 85505, "content": "你好美啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115714}, {"id": 85761, "content": "没有练瑜伽，还是给自己买了瑜伽服", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636624}, {"id": 86273, "content": "明明就是冷漠扑克脸却要装逗比 久了好像真的成了逗比", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473931}, {"id": 85250, "content": "别人说话的时候不断点头以表赞同", "image": "img/option/option/201607031259211lLW5HAOxwqynGRf.jpg", "praise_count": 147, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239957}, {"id": 85762, "content": "来泰国支教，在同事面前假装喜欢看泰剧，认识很多泰国明星，知道很多泰国的事……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205343}, {"id": 85251, "content": "做自己不喜欢的事情?", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488502}, {"id": 85507, "content": "是呢，真不知道他/她是怎么想的", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 9648}, {"id": 85763, "content": "倾听并认同", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579627}, {"id": 86275, "content": "刚毕业那年，装着会抽烟，在上班闲歇时跟两个同事在走廊抽两根", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435319}, {"id": 88067, "content": "微笑....点头...表示赞同", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643762}, {"id": 85252, "content": "不吱声", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635593}, {"id": 85508, "content": "穿上校服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636091}, {"id": 86276, "content": "逼自己喝酒，逼自己天天跟着他们参加各种酒局，说没头没脑的笑话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435319}, {"id": 105732, "content": "假装很认真的看别人眼睛，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677142}, {"id": 85253, "content": "做自己不喜欢的事情，还要装的很开心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488502}, {"id": 85509, "content": "笑，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593231}, {"id": 88837, "content": "我也是！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219928}, {"id": 85510, "content": "其实不喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628235}, {"id": 85766, "content": "哈 哈哈 哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594817}, {"id": 86022, "content": "啊！对对对对", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177018}, {"id": 85767, "content": "表现得很外向健谈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636654}, {"id": 85513, "content": "微笑+点头，必要时附和几句虽然不喜欢但也是没办法的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635493}, {"id": 85769, "content": "假装听得很认真，其实最后什么都没听懂，还得附和着傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469244}, {"id": 86537, "content": "装作无公害的样子……", "image": "img/option/option/201607021825117BqKoxYm4IJ6ELbt.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639498}, {"id": 85258, "content": "对啊 明明很无聊的谈话 却还要装作有兴趣的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635595}, {"id": 85514, "content": "不得不发内容差不多的票圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331292}, {"id": 85770, "content": "笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636663}, {"id": 85259, "content": "微笑的听着，偶尔说一句", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609479}, {"id": 85515, "content": "微笑不语", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166511}, {"id": 115467, "content": "打马虎眼的哈哈傻笑岔开话题略过伤心的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755861}, {"id": 85260, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613718}, {"id": 85772, "content": "我很正常", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636666}, {"id": 85517, "content": "朋友圈不提偶像，ktv不唱偶像", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613050}, {"id": 85262, "content": "呵呵\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613718}, {"id": 85518, "content": "假装合群的大笑，心里想的是这帮家伙到底笑点在哪", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568220}, {"id": 89358, "content": "做自己想做的\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647500}, {"id": 85263, "content": "笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633378}, {"id": 85775, "content": "假装喜欢big bang", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527345}, {"id": 85264, "content": "习惯性的周末一起打球，偶尔一起玩大家共同玩的游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621745}, {"id": 85776, "content": "也跟着一起打撸，虽然自己不喜欢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541262}, {"id": 85265, "content": "笑似乎是万能的，微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621745}, {"id": 85777, "content": "你说我附和。即使是陌生的领域也会微笑表示“我懂”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636674}, {"id": 89617, "content": "装傻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590799}, {"id": 85266, "content": "和自己不喜欢的人打交道，还要装作很开心……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635607}, {"id": 85522, "content": "装逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636109}, {"id": 88082, "content": "假笑，为了有存在感找缝插话表现", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643558}, {"id": 85267, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635608}, {"id": 85779, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585241}]}